As you read this letter, the words seem to leap off the page at you and become burned into your memory, almost as if you are reading about current events between us. Strix is sick and she is rapidly turning into a demon. Strix's goal is to beg Thorn to save her from her fate of being cursed to be a dragon. Strix must also urgently reach the punk venue to play an important set and claim the title of best band in Avernus.
